{"title":"TRANSFUSIÓN MASIVA-2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/TRANSFUSIÓN MASIVA-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"TRANSFUSIÓN\\NMASIVA","guid":"vcAaEGZ2qrqyd1JRjvlQng","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## DEFINICIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Transfusión de grandes volúmenes de productos sanguíneos en cortos períodos de tiempo a paciente con hemorragia severa no controlada.\\NLas cuatro definiciones más comunes son:","guid":"BVg2wGOi6ZfivA6FyGkH0w","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"1. Transfusión de 10-12 o más unidades de GR\\N(aproximadamente una volemia) en 24 horas","guid":"suchyP0PfmRKcYlv7HaXSA","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"- En niños: reemplazo de >1 volemia en 24 horas","guid":"tbKixQHQ_0x7D9fRl_Wwrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"2. Transfusión de más de 4 unidades de GR en 1 hora,\\Nanticipando necesidad de más productos","guid":"ZN-1iLObSA3WJkFaV2udQg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"3. Reemplazo de más del 50% de volumen sanguíneo total en 3 horas","guid":"A3JHBncs3P-zkSrx7PX1cQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"4. Pérdidas sanguíneas >150 ml/min","guid":"ae9rsBXAOIw3ILG2fCQUMA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"- En niños: 40 ml/kg de sangre o >10% volemia/minuto","guid":"pQ_MvJICbr89uxdvZ9cfcQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"## OBJETIVO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"- Estandarizar procedimientos para mejorar atención en hemorragias masivas","guid":"DCjsNJsBFsr9HOdc42Zc-w","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"- Promover reconocimiento temprano de necesidad de transfusión masiva","guid":"IEHmLD6vq-gk8Wh0-fuTYg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"- Optimizar uso de\\Ncomponentes sanguíneos","guid":"Q3SFy5U0KsiHzh9TryVNkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"## PREDICTORES\\NY ACTIVACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"### Score ABC\\N(más utilizado)","guid":"QPewqNCreZ2cUfp1eeXfeA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"- Puntuación: 1 punto por cada factor presente","guid":"7MpLgHxJJCvkRryRr9VAsg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"- ABC >2 indica alta probabilidad de transfusión masiva","guid":"r3RKsAg7p6huweZofbSt9g","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"- Factores:","guid":"6NOoAelp1lieBEg7iGhtQQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"- Trauma penetrante","guid":"mv76SoMm6f0P0huR-nLJIg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"- PAS <90","guid":"PavaN3VLa21HtY4ip6IQhQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"- FC >120","guid":"9KfbMTCfdg16xEtsbu9E4w","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"- Eco abdominal con líquido libre (FAST)","guid":"PJ8IItiz2CPPpMabQBTEGQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"13","text":"### Otros\\Npredictores","guid":"DqRkeLX67DrR_OizX9dP5g","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- INR >1.5 o ROTEM alterado","guid":"jaSpRfhpibClOsbmtqnu-g","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"- pH <7.2","guid":"__wUKGOVxVmxca_gWMP4CA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"- Déficit de base >6","guid":"-nS1XUiC1XhlunKVyeZRXw","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"- Lactato >4","guid":"r4Yum9yjXOLlj8wNfRaXNg","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"- Plaquetas <50.000/mm³","guid":"JSHpQYbDwB4lLjZwpddRdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"13","text":"### Índice\\Nde Shock","guid":"1_HBLsx1zoSwnzxvw9EKOg","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"- FC/PA sistólica (normal: 0.5-0.6)","guid":"uZTzHlkuUXrQ6DUgE0Wl6g","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"- 0.9-1.1: 1.5 veces más riesgo","guid":"0_Y-GBZ12-OhVeq_coaDZg","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"- 1.1-1.3: 5 veces más riesgo","guid":"rdhwadpGDTjtuzHgBxK5xQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"- >1.3: 8 veces más riesgo","guid":"8h1SyVEC1tlGf3r9k3r9yA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"## PROCEDIMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"1. Inicio por equipo de urgencia, UPC o pabellón","guid":"NzTRoeQCu_4XzbXNloIVYg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"2. Notificar a UMT (anexo 652729), laboratorio y UPC","guid":"WrTfHn232btJLxgLFK57ow","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"3. Proporcionar\\Ndatos del paciente:","guid":"JGvpAWjvOHkbgM4xDWH8fg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"- Nombre y apellidos","guid":"ACqtAtGh7g6ukrci6c8lUg","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"- Diagnóstico","guid":"kTGrG8tXGuv9OK5_x3mNsQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"- RUT (si es posible)","guid":"79z9-xDBPR5FAouX2uINnQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"- Localización","guid":"785-F5FWtrnvI8TgVs-aIQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"- Médico responsable","guid":"gOtjNdD7rdfKgzRlkAID7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"4. Tomar\\Nmuestras para:","guid":"XscUj9PrWfKm7ClXPi0IfA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"- Perfil hematológico","guid":"3iWo_b01o8C4-2tFMV0liw","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"- Lactato, pH y gases","guid":"cdmJBFZhQj1yOKYAa5ikKg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"- Pruebas de coagulación","guid":"bQybc2Gi11B-Odb-gnkB8A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"- Grupo sanguíneo y Rh","guid":"idLaoyzYjKo5LzM6LArbLw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"- ROTEM","guid":"AwAKhJKJxcBfh76Obim2Rg","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"33","text":"5. UMT enviará 2 unidades GR O RhD(-)\\Nsin cruzar inmediatamente","guid":"6diIwl4WboKX-j94IzSXvg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"33","text":"6. Enviar solicitud de transfusión inmediata","guid":"VJ9PdWA2QmBdJ8-2ejAKRQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"33","text":"7. Administrar ácido tranexámico (antes de 3 horas post-trauma)","guid":"JzEoilzHGDWOSNNmSPHW3w","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"33","text":"8. TM guiada por ROTEM o paquetes predefinidos","guid":"KR-PkM93uEtmENiiTLnTjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"## PAQUETES DE\\NTRANSFUSIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"### Adultos\\N(relación 1:1:1)","guid":"3FOjrna5XXkax7FfXvxEXw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"1° paquete: 4U GR + 600ml PFC + 1 pool plaquetas (6U)","guid":"F3o3USZDAzlwhOnTlDG5Dw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"2° paquete: 4U GR + 600ml PFC","guid":"PXdg3psR8HI07QUexv2LVw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"3° paquete: 4U GR + 600ml PFC + 1 pool plaquetas (6U)","guid":"JokigsdtzCgiwr-1biDceA","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"4° paquete: 4U GR + 600ml PFC","guid":"jJwFLngm_XZ-2ZRnjm5a9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"52","text":"### Niños\\N(primer paquete)","guid":"KD_v7KQHjjkbyG8aCKFCyQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- <20kg: 2U GR (20ml/kg) + 2U PFC (20ml/kg) + 2U plaquetas (1U/10kg)","guid":"N8PRhPI8TjFlVLpbD6S6eg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- 20-40kg: 3U GR + 3U PFC + 4U plaquetas (1/2 aféresis)","guid":"cnq9syUCgScchhuJGTBuDw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"- >40kg: 4U GR + 4U PFC + 6U plaquetas (1 aféresis)","guid":"XXx-F69P2weO_X5kC_2RBA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"## UMBRALES\\NTRANSFUSIONALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"- Hemoglobina: 7-9 g/dl","guid":"DI3drOIuT4tbm1WckrXehg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"- INR: <1.5","guid":"Za3bYLiloJYCi--kI08rXA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"- Plaquetas: >50.000 (>100.000 en TCE)","guid":"wDgqbTI_upg8z29YWHXk0Q","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"- Fibrinógeno: >2g/dL","guid":"4kP52MoDC_PrwhdTVHABIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"## FÁRMACOS\\NHEMOSTÁTICOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"- Ácido tranexámico: 1g IV en 10 min + 1g en 8h (antes de 3h post-trauma)","guid":"claH4FC9Y-H0Tw7AV3iWrg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"- Factor VIIr: 60-90 μg/kg en casos refractarios","guid":"YbOwP8mxokTaUbxW3xS1Ng","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"- Concentrado complejo protrombínico: 15-30 U/kg según INR","guid":"oPT88kFXJGe5JjFkLeQ4Vg","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"- Concentrado de fibrinógeno: mantener niveles 1.5-2.0 g/L","guid":"DVE6CkX5_IZSa4BA-UNuLQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"- Control de calcio iónico (<1 mmol/L)","guid":"gcJzUutfayUT_900wIELPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"##\\NCONSIDERACIONES\\NESPECIALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- La hemodilución por cristaloides agrava la coagulopatía","guid":"qpvXB6_f_KtOlNlQvAYj5w","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"- El manejo debe realizarse en el punto de atención","guid":"QC_v44AAMrwAHQerw_ywJQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"- Detener el sangrado es prioritario","guid":"CTtDy5b51Z7vC9xFfJMx6A","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"- Vigilar la \"tríada letal\": coagulopatía, hipotermia y acidosis","guid":"3KKiilBbBup9DG8hWs5JfQ","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"- Realizar analítica seriada cada 30/60/120 minutos","guid":"dS5NLycMcJ6BrVj1OTBLuA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"- El médico responsable comunicará finalización del protocolo","guid":"JYrhVtiw71Tx9vFvwWYg2w","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":79,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"TRANSFUSIÓN MASIVA-2025-1","id":"map_1096","resolved_references":[]}